about: Flow is a design and motion studio that brings brands and stories to life. As a values-driven studio, we focus on purpose-driven campaigns, collaborating extensively in the third sector, as well as with innovative organisations in tech, education and healthcare.

From syncing digital and in-store experiences to sustainable practices and optimising spend, we tackle the challenges your CMO loses sleep over.

Want a brand that stands out? We’re ready to bring the heat.

Shaping distinctive brands for commercial & cultural impact, Halo is a creative studio specialising in strategy, storytelling and creativity. We turn bold ambition into reality, with insight driven, original ideas that look great and people love.

Fiercely independent for 20 years, we work for household names and ambitious challengers; approaching all projects with acuity and agility, focusing on what matters most, maximising investment, bringing an open mind and original ideas to every brief.

Whatever your mission, we’ve been opening doors to audiences both new and old, delivering successful results for 25 years. We’re experts at defining and delivering on your brands promise, and at identifying the best ways to turn your goals a reality.
